INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("139", "1", "2016-09-27 15:47:00", "2016-09-27 15:47:00", "<img class=\"wp-image-141 alignright\" src=\"http://localhost/rainbow/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/rainbow-in-sight-counselling-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"rainbow-in-sight-counselling\" width=\"277\" height=\"184\" />\r\n\r\nAs a therapist with over 20 years experience, something my clients always comment on is how quickly they feel comfortable talking to me about their issues. A safe and caring environment where youre able to talk freely about your personal problems without fear of judgment or criticism is always provided.\r\n\r\nYour unique needs and respecting the situation youre in are my highest priorities. My diverse background allows me to tailor my style of working with you so you get exactly the right type of support you need.\r\n\r\nWhen youre ready to reach out for the support you need, it is with a sense of great privilage, trust and respect I will meet you. And when the positive change youre working towards starts to happen, this for me is the greatest reward.\r\n\r\nYou may feel a sense of great relief even after your first session, simply because youve found such a safe place, where youre working together with someone in a solution focused way to resolve your issues. You can finally see light at the end of the tunnel.\r\n\r\nSo give me a call, in the strictest confidence and lets start working together towards positive change.", "Helping People For 20 Years", "", "publish", "open", "open", "", "helping-people-for-20-years", "", "", "2016-09-27 15:48:55", "2016-09-27 15:48:55", "", "0", "http://localhost/rainbow/?p=139", "0", "post", "", "0");
